queries.sql: SELECT status, COUNT(*) AS total FROM ( SELECT s.student_id, CASE WHEN COUNT(a.attendance_id) = 0 THEN 'Absent' WHEN MAX(CASE WHEN a.remarks = 'IN' THEN a.time END) IS NOT NULL AND MAX(CASE WHEN a.remarks = 'OUT' THEN a.time END) IS NOT NULL THEN 'Present' ELSE 'Incomplete' END AS status FROM students s LEFT JOIN attendance a ON s.student_id = a.student_id AND a.date = '2025-11-26' WHERE s.is_enroll=1 GROUP BY s.student_id ) AS sub GROUP BY status
